1928   // incoming values that comes from the same block and this specific constant
1929   // value can be used to do optimization for specific binary operator.
1930   // For example:
1931   // %phi0 = phi i32 [0, %bb0], [%i, %bb1]
1932   // %phi1 = phi i32 [%j, %bb0], [0, %bb1]
1933   // %add = add i32 %phi0, %phi1
1934   // ==>
1935   // %add = phi i32 [%j, %bb0], [%i, %bb1]
